# MTLDynamicLibraryError.Code.compilationFailure

**Case**

An error code that indicates Metal couldn’t compile a dynamic library.

## Declaration

```swift
case compilationFailure
```

## Error codes

- **MTLDynamicLibraryError.Code.none**: An error code that represents the absence of any problems.
- **MTLDynamicLibraryError.Code.invalidFile**: An error code that indicates an app is using an invalid reference to a library file, typically related to a URL.
- **MTLDynamicLibraryError.Code.unresolvedInstallName**: An error code that indicates Metal couldn’t resolve the installation name for a new dynamic library.
- **MTLDynamicLibraryError.Code.dependencyLoadFailure**: An error code that indicates a dynamic library couldn’t link to other dynamic libraries.
- **MTLDynamicLibraryError.Code.unsupported**: An error code that indicates the GPU device doesn’t support dynamic libraries.
